name: collectors blockchain
description: An interactive drawing experiment. You have two options: collect or swap the piece. Each time you collect it, a block will be added to your link in the chain (to a max of 6). If you swap one of your editions, your link and the subsequent links in the chain will be rotated 90 degrees. Note that this NFT is quite experimental an it might break in the future. Creator: Javier Gracia Carpio | @jagracar
